{"tid":1408363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地只要對準政權同黑警黑社會，我地做好多野都有人支持","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:36:49.000Z","uid":37528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0475acd7bd84bc305b6d3be853c1b4f8b2025e96","tid":1408363,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:07:54.000Z","msg":"只要我地對準呢三大害，香港人普遍支持<br />\n至於當中有好多藍絲爪牙，其實唔需要特別在意，好似今日個黃大仙的士佬咁，撚佢兩下俾佢走就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(當然學天琦話齋最好就可以令佢支持我地)<br />\n仲有今次發現好多受阻人士，即使係司機乘客都支持我地(尋日有個中旅旅遊車司機都支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，我地唔可以流失佢地既支持，我地先有勝算<br />\n仲有影相問題，我地戴好曬口罩，就唔好太在意其他人影相拍片，就算真係叫人唔好影，都好聲好氣少少，明白大家抗爭都會攰同燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然如果有人影大頭就另計<br />\n<br />\n我地而家面對緊全世界最大黑社會，爭取緊一d佢唔會俾我地既野，我地要贏就要鬥智鬥力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家要對準：港共政權，黑警，黑社會</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9284ebee85c03b4d3191f85d69034078ed9530","tid":1408363,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0017f49272783f82261eba6c8811cac80d4d898f","tid":1408363,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29546e63c95b983065